{"tid":228411,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"ASUS Router 58U 成日斷線","createTime":"2017-05-04T00:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T10:48:17.000Z","uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6c9c7d4693e524550e55a2e7cd019182b6ada42e","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:18:44.000Z","msg":"用緊netvigator 500mb光纖 <br />\n<br />\n而家係 modem---router(放wifi同LAN)---PC 咁樣駁<br />\n<br />\n打機成日斷線好麻煩 又冇改善<br />\n<br />\n1）有冇巴打用緊58U都會有呢個問題？有的話又點整返好？<br />\n<br />\n另外想問 2）可唔可以 modem---PC(LAN 線)---router(淨放wifi) 咁樣駁？因為modem直插電腦完全冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望巴絲賜教 給予我不斷線的人生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae197f8fdf2c6bb18075ef5a2c914f22734714c","tid":228411,"uid":40308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:28:30.000Z","msg":"你係近排先有哩個問題定不嬲係咁？<br />\n最近有無update個router?"},{"pid":"15cd81dd5a3ba94284f12edaa63bfb8b591cc7e3","tid":228411,"uid":95360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:30:07.000Z","msg":"1：冇用緊，但呢D問題可以試下Reset router / upgrade firmware / 2.4g/5g wifi 分返開2個名, 先試分名<br />\n<br />\n2；唔得，因為Modem default 出1個ip"},{"pid":"2b7fc329a1e03d59f8fdb37b5a20d69dee365653","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係近排先有哩個問題定不嬲係咁？<br />\n最近有無update個router?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n之前用netvigator 8mb都有斷斷地 但唔會好似而家一斷就10-15min<br />\n<br />\nRouter firmware 係 asus網係最新<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3eb114da0d26098569150cb7473cfc2b8b11304","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:47:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1：冇用緊，但呢D問題可以試下Reset router / upgrade firmware / 2.4g/5g wifi 分返開2個名, 先試分名<br />\n<br />\n2；唔得，因為Modem default 出1個ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家試reset先 唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e400058acbf8ea14b67d7c3bff53e1663d67d9","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T00:49:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1：冇用緊，但呢D問題可以試下Reset router / upgrade firmware / 2.4g/5g wifi 分返開2個名, 先試分名<br />\n<br />\n2；唔得，因為Modem default 出1個ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來係因為得1個 IP<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲以為買張 external internet adapter 就可以拎router插電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4021301e260852677e6eef15f6a69b2e00cb7310","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"會唔會因為太多人連wifi而斷線？<br />\n<br />\n5人屋企 最高峰應該有5-8部會同時上網<br />\n計埋待機的話 一共有10-13部device"},{"pid":"756d9b0ef47ea9540bd7786c82d4704f010382bc","tid":228411,"uid":95360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T01:37:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>會唔會因為太多人連wifi而斷線？<br />\n<br />\n5人屋企 最高峰應該有5-8部會同時上網<br />\n計埋待機的話 一共有10-13部device</blockquote><br />\n正常Asus唔會呢個數都做唔到<br />\n除非你自己打細個Dhcp pool<br />\nBtw 5人屋企你 wifi會唔會係唔夠coverage先斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bd9c006bab2dfa0b72bcff02ac543ece9528f76","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>會唔會因為太多人連wifi而斷線？<br />\n<br />\n5人屋企 最高峰應該有5-8部會同時上網<br />\n計埋待機的話 一共有10-13部device</blockquote><br />\n正常Asus唔會呢個數都做唔到<br />\n除非你自己打細個Dhcp pool<br />\nBtw 5人屋企你 wifi會唔會係唔夠coverage先斷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n應該唔關coverage事<br />\n<br />\n因為佢一斷會斷曬lan線同wifi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw 多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8964258ced084f264131259d437a52ae511bf1d","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:38:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1：冇用緊，但呢D問題可以試下Reset router / upgrade firmware / 2.4g/5g wifi 分返開2個名, 先試分名<br />\n<br />\n2；唔得，因為Modem default 出1個ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家試reset先 唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nReset 完玩overwatch都成日斷線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ed443e5c4313e50c0325a77b3fb1f1be861744e","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1：冇用緊，但呢D問題可以試下Reset router / upgrade firmware / 2.4g/5g wifi 分返開2個名, 先試分名<br />\n<br />\n2；唔得，因為Modem default 出1個ip</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家試reset先 唔該絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nReset 完玩overwatch都成日斷線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/04/214101_e69ca631e970f537f3c26e660eb7db92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F04%2F214101_e69ca631e970f537f3c26e660eb7db92.jpg&h=100ada19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係21:38時同幾分鐘前（唔知2133/2137時）都斷過<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲幫到小弟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dab08231d34eec1b8546586de9e262d857be442c","tid":228411,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:20:42.000Z","msg":"router   有冇過熱<br />\n啲線夠唔夠食個 bandwidth<br />\n有冇裝大陸野"},{"pid":"9a9e70c723dbef67d526ca30f40d553678a27efe","tid":228411,"uid":99302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:22:28.000Z","msg":"試下直連modem先"},{"pid":"e039848dc7fa3294e02c23c6145771231f161496","tid":228411,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:24:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試下直連modem先</blockquote><br />\n佢有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6247ed47e3327d73762e2dd3bbe95a9028b36f28","tid":228411,"uid":71937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:25:52.000Z","msg":"&lt;路過&gt;<br />\n我隻58U 行LAN會變左Self-Assigned IP, 反而Wifi無事，reset/update firmware都搞佢唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d1102955d74ba3c024df65af385c2046c417aa1","tid":228411,"uid":44917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"我有時都無啦啦會斷線 要重開部機<br />\n好唔好拎去ASUS維修下呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebfd9e5c6b7c3bdfd5b3d1cd5b8c87ed73c5ea94","tid":228411,"uid":12231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T13:03:02.000Z","msg":"今日打咁去問asus 佢幾肯定係isp供應商出事 唔關router事<br />\n<br />\n多謝上面咁多位巴絲的解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nASUS啲人勁好禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nNetvigator啲人真係西到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788e247ff153aae57ee40aa7500ce25c1ad271b8","tid":228411,"uid":34145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>今日打咁去問asus 佢幾肯定係isp供應商出事 唔關router事<br />\n<br />\n多謝上面咁多位巴絲的解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nASUS啲人勁好禮貌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla